description: This common Plezier purrs with a rating of 55, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 110, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 5 for North, 1 for East, 5 for South, and Leverage for West. Plezier has the personality suit of yenta. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Plezier [110 Votes, Common]
